<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1963">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$sousou" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/sousou" class="zg-link" title="诚Sousou">诚Sousou</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-fei-61-41" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-fei-61-41" class="zg-link" title="小飞">小飞</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$san-kou-70" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/san-kou-70" class="zg-link" title="三口">三口</a></span>
